quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,102,"La yasmaAAoona haseesahawahum fee ma ishtahat anfusuhum khalidoon"
  21,103,"La yahzunuhumu alfazaAAual-akbaru watatalaqqahumu almala-ikatu hathayawmukumu allathee kuntum tooAAadoon"
  21,104,"Yawma natwee assamaakatayyi assijlli lilkutubi kama bada/naawwala khalqin nuAAeeduhu waAAdan AAalayna innakunna faAAileen"
  21,105,"Walaqad katabna fee azzaboorimin baAAdi aththikri anna al-arda yarithuhaAAibadiya assalihoon"
  21,106,"Inna fee hatha labalaghanliqawmin AAabideen"
  21,107,"Wama arsalnaka illa rahmatanlilAAalameen"
  21,108,"Qul innama yooha ilayya annamailahukum ilahun wahidun fahal antummuslimoon"
  21,109,"Fa-in tawallaw faqul athantukum AAalasawa-in wa-in adree aqareebun am baAAeedun matooAAadoon"
  21,110,"Innahu yaAAlamu aljahra mina alqawliwayaAAlamu ma taktumoon"
  21,111,"Wa-in adree laAAallahu fitnatun lakum wamataAAunila heen"
  21,112,"Qala rabbi ohkum bilhaqqiwarabbuna arrahmanu almustaAAanuAAala ma tasifoon"
